OL,5, It's been nearly 13 years since the    
OL,6, devastating earthquake and tsunami that
OL,7, triggered an accident at a nuclear     
OL,8, plant in Fukushima.                    
OL,10,FBut memories in Japan are still fresh. 
OL,11,FAnd on Monday, all of them will have   
OL,12,Fbeen brought back in to focus as the   
OL,13,Fshaking began in Ishikawa and the      
OL,14,Ftsunami alarms began sounding.         
OL,16,FThe warnings are not exactly unusual in
OL,17,FJapan.                                 
OL,19,FWhen I first moved there, I would leap 
OL,20,Fout of bed at the slightest shaking of 
OL,21,Four building.                          
